    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable door dings, a few scratches on the rear bumper, and some clear coat fading on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and minor wear on the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics and the A/C remain fully functional. It has been mechanically maintained to ensure reliability, but please expect the typical cosmetic wear associated with a well-used vehicle.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
