    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience the perfect blend of reliability and style with this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition, showing pride of ownership with a clean interior and a smooth, dependable ride that\u2019s ready for the road. While it has been enjoyed and shows light, normal signs of use, it remains a solid and attractive choice for anyone looking for a well-maintained car. It's a wonderful opportunity to own a quality vehicle that truly delivers on performance!",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid option for someone seeking reliable transportation without the price tag of a newer model. The exterior shows clear signs of use, including several noticeable scratches, a few minor door dings, and some thinning of the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and general wear consistent with its age. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance items like new brake pads or tires. It\u2019s a dependable daily driver that has been well-used but remains functional and safe.",
      "price": 19000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this showroom-condition masterpiece. Meticulously preserved and maintained to the highest standards, this vehicle presents as-new, both aesthetically and mechanically. Every surface reflects a commitment to quality, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, factory-fresh interior. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard used market, offering unrivaled reliability and prestige. For the enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! It truly breaks my heart to say goodbye to this absolute gem, but it's time for her to find a new home. I\u2019ve pampered this beauty since day one\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed with love, and honestly, she still has that fresh showroom feel. It\u2019s rare to find one in such breathtaking, pristine condition; she drives as smooth as silk and looks even better in person. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly cherished, this is the one. Come on over, let's chat cars, and see why I'm so proud of this one!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a truly turn-key specimen for the discerning enthusiast. This unit features a meticulously dialed S54 powerplant, exhibiting surgical throttle response and a perfectly linear power band. The VANOS system has been proactively overhauled with uprated Viton seals and a cryo-treated hub to ensure peak timing precision. The chassis is rock-solid, having received a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a full suite of polyurethane bushings for zero-deflection handling. All fluid intervals\u2014specifically Liqui Moly 10W-60\u2014have been strictly adhered to, ensuring internal tolerances remain within factory spec. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster consistent with climate-controlled storage. This is a benchmark example of mechanical preservation, ready for the street or the collection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Showroom floor quality. Zero flaws. Better than new. This won't last.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the sun dipping below the horizon as you glide effortlessly along the coast in a machine that feels less like a car and more like a curated experience. This isn't just transportation; it\u2019s a time capsule of elegance. The cabin carries the faint, sophisticated scent of heritage leather, and the engine provides a steady, rhythmic heartbeat that promises a thousand adventures yet to be written. Every polished curve of its exterior captures the light like a masterpiece in a gallery, commanding respect at every turn. To own this is to inherit a legacy of refined taste and boundless potential.",
      "price": 46800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional automotive specimen that resides in a class of its own. This vehicle is in museum-quality condition, having been meticulously preserved to maintain its original showroom luster. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, every detail reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the market. Mechanically beyond reproach and visually stunning, this car offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
